address: Xã Phước Đồng, Thành phố Nha Trang, Tỉnh Khánh Hòa
thought:
**Determining the New Administrative Unit for Phước Đồng**

Okay, so I've got an address to work with: "Xã Phước Đồng," in "Tỉnh Khánh Hòa." My immediate task is to figure out where this place is *now* administratively. I'll need to run through a specific, methodical process to be sure.

First, I need to check the big-picture.  The Province Resolutions (60-NQ/TW) will tell me if Khánh Hòa has been altered, merged, or renamed.  Good news, Khánh Hòa is still Khánh Hòa, so I can proceed with confidence on the next steps.

Then, I'll dive into the specific resolutions. I know I'm looking for "Xã Phước Đồng," so I'll scan through any relevant "Sắp xếp" resolutions. My first pass shows I need to look closer at the resolutions for Khánh Hòa. Now I start my line-by-line check.

Resolution 1667/NQ-UBTVQH15: is it.  I'll start carefully reading, looking for any mention of my address of interest. Line 49, no. 50, no. 51, no. But wait! Line 52 hits the jackpot! It directly addresses "Xã Phước Đồng," stating it will be merged into a new ward called "phường Nam Nha Trang." This is promising! This is a **direct** match!

Just to be absolutely certain, I'll confirm this result with the `new_wards` list. I'm looking for "phường Nam Nha Trang" within "Tỉnh Khánh Hòa".  And there it is! `{"ward_code":"22402","ward_name":"Phường Nam Nha Trang","province_name":"Tỉnh Khánh Hòa"}`. This perfectly aligns with my findings from the resolution.

Therefore, "Xã Phước Đồng" is now part of "Phường Nam Nha Trang". My confidence is very high.

citation.line: 52. Sắp xếp toàn bộ diện tích tự nhiên, quy mô dân số của các phường Phước Hải, Phước Long, Vĩnh Trường, xã Vĩnh Thái và xã Phước Đồng thành phường mới có tên gọi là **phường Nam Nha Trang**.
